Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.06,0:01:34.52,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ladies and gentlemen,\ngood evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.16,0:01:39.19,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,At Luna's Carnival, I encountered\nan immature soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.10,0:01:45.59,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My friend said to me, "This shall be\nthe prelude to my vengeance."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.27,0:01:49.00,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But this soul was too young\nand beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.58,0:01:53.88,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It is that alone which\ngives me cause for fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.02,0:02:02.99,count fo,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(353,350)}Act 2:\NUntil the Sun Rises Over the Moon
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.23,0:02:16.36,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to come?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.64,0:02:21.30,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough\nfun and games, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.89,0:02:43.38,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you met him\nthe other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.73,0:02:48.63,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you bored?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.40,0:02:51.80,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all. It's a wonderful party,\ndon't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.87,0:02:54.20,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Where is your friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.31,0:02:55.57,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you mean Albert?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.34,0:02:59.90,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He's probably out trying to pick up girls, and\ngetting turned down by every one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.01,0:03:02.98,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But this is terrible!\NThis is Luna!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.18,0:03:06.41,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Strolling around alone at\Nnight is tantamount to suicide!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.52,0:03:07.78,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Surely you're exaggerating...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.89,0:03:12.92,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's no laughing matter.\NYou'll get kidnapped by Luigi Vampa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.69,0:03:15.13,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Luigi Vampa?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.50,0:03:17.43,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He's an up-and-coming\nbandit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.73,0:03:20.20,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They say that he drags his victims\ninto the catacombs,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.30,0:03:22.96,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...tortures them,\nand finally kills them!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.10,0:03:24.43,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How horrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.70,0:03:26.87,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Surely the police won't\nstand by and do nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.94,0:03:28.37,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.71,0:03:32.54,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The police on Luna arrange\ntheir patrols to avoid the bandits.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.85,0:03:39.48,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My very own cousin was robbed blind,\nhad his arms and legs broken,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.59,0:03:42.55,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and was left stark naked\nin the plaza!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.69,0:03:45.66,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All because he spoke\nto the bandit's mistress!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.09,0:03:50.29,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he's fine. I bet that he's back\nat your hotel at this very moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.63,0:03:52.00,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Would you care\nto dance?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.30,0:03:59.53,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I simply despise when\na party ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.07,0:04:04.20,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,First one guest leaves, then two.\NEspecially at this hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.04,0:04:08.71,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You won't abandon me,\nwill you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.92,0:04:46.32,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Take him away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.90,0:05:00.83,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You can't! It's mean!\NToday is my birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.57,0:05:05.03,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Franz.\NI have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.14,0:05:06.60,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.71,0:05:10.11,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Your father is leaving to see to\nsome very important business.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.44,0:05:13.34,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, see if I care! I hope\nyou never come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.06,0:05:25.52,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.60,0:05:34.96,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm sorry.\NDid I keep you waiting long?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.43,0:05:37.96,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I... think I should go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.44,0:05:47.41,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you Baron\NFranz d'Epinay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.48,0:05:51.55,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.55,0:05:53.02,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sick of\nyour whining!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.69,0:05:57.66,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,As for me, I killed\nten people!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.46,0:06:01.69,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.80,0:06:05.49,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,"My Lord Baron\NFranz d'Epinay."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.13,0:06:12.33,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,"I, Luigi Vampa, have taken custody of\nyour friend, the Viscount Albert Morcerf."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.87,0:06:17.28,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,"Hand over the sum of 50 million ducats\nto my messenger immediately."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.64,0:06:20.44,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,"If the messenger should\nnot return by sunrise,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.55,0:06:24.14,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,"...although it pains me to do so,\nthink of your friend's life as forfeit."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.42,0:06:25.32,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Albert?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.42,0:06:30.32,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He's a valuable hostage, so we're\ntaking real good care of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.49,0:06:35.12,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If the money is handed over, he'll be sent\nhome without so much as a scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.23,0:06:38.42,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You should have died!\NIs this how you people do things?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.60,0:06:43.26,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Even I have a certain\nlifestyle to maintain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.37,0:06:44.96,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,50 million\nis absurd!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.57,0:06:49.30,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that a Parisian aristocrat won't be\nhard pressed to come up with such a sum.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.18,0:06:52.54,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Dawn comes fast\non Luna.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.78,0:06:55.01,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you value your\nfriend's life,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.11,0:06:57.64,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...I suggest that you make arrangements\nfor the money as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.49,0:07:02.65,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I want to make an immediate withdrawal\nfrom the Bank of Paris!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.76,0:07:04.25,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm terribly sorry,\nsir,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.36,0:07:09.45,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...but our connection to Europe is currently\noffline due to solar winds.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.06,0:07:11.53,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there anything\nyou can do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.26,0:07:13.53,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How much does\nsir require?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.63,0:07:44.19,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Albert... Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.43,0:07:50.23,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Say, son, it's awfully sad to see a young fella like\nyourself all alone on the last night of Carnival.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.60,0:07:54.00,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you want, I know\na fine girl who...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.11,0:07:56.04,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please, just be quiet\nand drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.24,0:08:02.24,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It was at my father's funeral\nthat I first met Albert...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.50,0:08:25.03,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.14,0:08:26.50,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not crying...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.87,0:08:28.46,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll play with you,\nso cheer up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.57,0:08:30.60,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Leave me alone!\NGet lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.15,0:08:38.81,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.45,0:08:46.79,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since that day, Albert\Nand I have been inseparable.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.07,0:09:00.33,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! What am I\ngoing to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.32,0:09:20.42,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost sunrise!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.83,0:09:24.49,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Have you raised\nthe money yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.60,0:09:25.50,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Give me more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.60,0:09:27.96,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Once it's morning, I'll have the\nmoney transferred from Paris!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.07,0:09:32.70,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Luigi is a stickler\nfor punctuality.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.81,0:09:38.33,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't have the money ready by sunrise,\nyour friend is a goner.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.44,0:09:39.78,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Stop messing\nwith me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.11,0:09:41.81,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I suggest that\nyou hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.45,0:09:47.11,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that you don't want to see your\nfriend die a horrible death, My Lord Baron.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.39,0:09:48.41,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.99,0:09:55.22,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Violence is unseemly,\NMy Lord Baron.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.83,0:09:57.96,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.93,0:10:04.89,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's better. A gentleman has\Nto worry about little things like discretion.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.95,0:10:18.47,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There is no more fascinating spectacle\nthan a man's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.78,0:10:25.38,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it almost feels as if one has\nbecome God, does it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.79,0:10:31.29,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,His Excellency,\nthe Baron d'Epinay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.43,0:10:36.73,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry to disturb you\nat such an hour...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.54,0:10:42.84,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is something the matter?\NYou do not seem entirely well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.54,0:10:47.88,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Count! I have a favor\nto ask of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.79,0:11:01.16,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's the big idea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.99,0:11:03.83,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There is your\N50 million ducats.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.06,0:11:06.86,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now, you will take us\nto the hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.95,0:11:22.31,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,To the Colosseum!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.03,0:11:36.76,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Have the two of you been\nfriends for a long time?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.46,0:11:41.40,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we've been best friends\nsince we were children.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.37,0:11:44.89,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, so you are\nchildhood friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.07,0:11:47.73,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Constant friendship...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.94,0:11:52.04,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It is a wonderful thing,\nis it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.28,0:11:58.68,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you like?\NC'mon, tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.78,0:12:00.65,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,At least give me\na hint!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.45,0:12:03.65,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.43,0:12:15.53,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Luigi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.00,0:12:18.94,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.51,0:12:24.91,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.48,0:12:30.41,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So, have you made\nyour peace?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.28,0:12:33.65,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, ma'am,\nlet me kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.75,0:12:34.84,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, let me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.95,0:12:36.44,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, give it a rest,\nyou two!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.56,0:12:39.18,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You can carve him up as much\Nas you want after he's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.83,0:12:44.69,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then. You should put up\na brave front while you still can.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.03,0:12:47.90,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what you'll sound like\nwhen you cry?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.27,0:12:56.10,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.84,0:13:00.68,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Visitors to\nsee the boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.91,0:13:03.64,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.72,0:13:14.59,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Teresa, don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.79,0:13:16.82,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We can't kill him yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.36,0:13:19.30,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,B-Because we won't get\nthe money!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.57,0:13:22.66,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And besides... There's still\na little time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.77,0:13:23.89,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Stand aside!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.00,0:13:25.66,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to use that,\nuse it on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.07,0:13:28.44,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Squabbling among yourselves\nis pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.17,0:13:31.04,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.\NStand back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.28,0:13:33.18,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to disgrace\nthe boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.75,0:13:35.68,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine. Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.49,0:13:43.11,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So, does that mean\nyou've fallen for that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.29,0:13:47.19,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's so sweet...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.59,0:13:51.53,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But she's too much for you\nto handle, little boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.70,0:13:57.90,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe... you'd rather become\none of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.87,0:14:04.60,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I think I'll brand you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.42,0:14:13.85,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.02,0:14:16.15,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Leave her alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.25,0:14:46.15,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I have come to meet with Signor Luigi Vampa,\nwhose reputation is notorious on Luna.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.45,0:14:47.82,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.59,0:14:53.25,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My name is... Gankutsuou.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.46,0:14:57.43,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,T-The King\nof the Cave?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.26,0:15:01.32,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,For one such as yourself who\ndwells in the darkness,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.73,0:15:04.26,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...I expect that I am better\nknown by that name.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.97,0:15:08.77,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I have your money.\NNow, hand over the hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.21,0:15:11.44,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but you missed\nthe deadline.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.78,0:15:15.58,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,"Always be punctual,"\nthat's my motto.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.42,0:15:20.94,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,"Punctuality is the politeness\nof kings," is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.59,0:15:27.05,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm deeply honored... by your\ngracious words!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.17,0:15:44.27,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I see... Your skill\nis impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.91,0:15:49.35,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But you cannot kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.08,0:15:54.31,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you...\NAre you really...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.35,0:15:58.41,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you really him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.09,0:16:02.25,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I do not work for\nthe authorities.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.67,0:16:10.07,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you would do me the honor\nof returning my friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.40,0:16:11.63,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...all will be well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.41,0:16:24.38,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't injured, I take it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.78,0:16:29.78,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I had a feeling that you\nwould come to rescue me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.72,0:16:34.21,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you wish to thank someone,\Nthank the good Baron d'Epinay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.99,0:16:37.99,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He was gravely concerned\nfor your wellbeing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.17,0:16:45.76,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.20,0:16:47.33,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.21,0:16:54.27,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Say, I never asked you\nwhat your name was...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.88,0:17:01.25,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Albert.\NAlbert de Morcerf.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.79,0:17:03.78,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Peppo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.67,0:17:21.80,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,To tell you the truth, I was almost considering\nthrowing in my lot with the bandits.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.28,0:17:26.30,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you're all right, Albert.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.85,0:17:29.21,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What took you\nso long, Franz?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.45,0:17:33.75,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I came this close to being killed,\nyou know!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.76,0:17:41.09,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I was seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.80,0:17:50.77,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What was that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.87,0:17:57.60,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please, do not concern yourselves\nover the matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.74,0:18:01.04,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It served as a pleasant\ndiversion for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.15,0:18:03.14,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But I have to do something\nto repay you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.28,0:18:08.58,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, might I ask\none favor of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.86,0:18:11.72,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Anything at all!\NJust name it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.22,0:18:16.96,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I should like to take up\Nresidence in Paris at some point.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.60,0:18:19.03,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.93,0:18:24.70,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,However, a rustic aristocrat such as myself\nhas no connections in Paris.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.24,0:18:30.50,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,As such, might I impose on you to act as\nmy intermediary into Parisian society?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.74,0:18:32.18,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Think nothing of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.91,0:18:40.11,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I shall call on you on\NMay 22nd, three months from this day,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.45,0:18:44.08,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...to commemorate the\nevents of this day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.03,0:18:48.96,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Where in the world\ndid you find this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.09,0:18:51.65,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I found it.\NAt the opera house.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.10,0:18:53.53,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so that is\nwhere it was!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.87,0:18:57.56,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It shames me to say it,\Nbut I have looked everywhere for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.84,0:19:00.27,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This, too, shows that there\nis some bond between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.47,0:19:04.10,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please accept it\nwith my gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.28,0:19:07.18,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Think of it as a small token\nof our friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.05,0:19:09.34,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.68,0:19:12.58,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It will serve to freeze the memory\nof this day, this hour, in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.92,0:19:15.51,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A memory which belongs\nto us alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.06,0:19:19.89,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much!\NI'll cherish it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.36,0:19:25.92,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Carnival has ended, so what\nare your plans now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.43,0:19:30.60,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to cut our trip short and\ntake the evening shuttle back to Paris.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.80,0:19:35.33,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait a minute!\NI've already made plans of my own!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.87,0:19:39.83,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You never learn, do you?\NAnd what "plans" might these be?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.38,0:19:43.64,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?\NIt's none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.45,0:19:48.25,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Have you arranged\na rendezvous, perhaps?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.25,0:19:50.81,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sort of...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.36,0:19:54.26,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Love is a\nwonderful thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.06,0:19:59.00,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,However, perhaps you\nhave not noticed yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.33,0:20:03.27,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Or perhaps you knew, and\Narranged the rendezvous regardless.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.70,0:20:06.47,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I do hate to be the bearer\nof bad tidings, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.64,0:20:12.84,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.25,0:20:14.77,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She's a boy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.48,0:20:19.78,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come out and say it! You think\NI'm an idiot, don't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.89,0:20:20.94,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.09,0:20:24.18,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're always looking down on me,\nlaughing at me on the inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.06,0:20:28.58,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not laughing\nat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.99,0:20:32.52,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If I laughed at every boneheaded stunt\nyou pulled, I'd bust a gut!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.50,0:20:35.33,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, you were...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.50,0:20:39.94,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.77,0:20:42.50,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I owe you my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.18,0:20:47.08,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.63,0:21:07.76,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The fruits of betrayal must\Nbe plucked from the tree...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.96,0:23:15.89,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,At long last, the appointed day arrives.\NHe comes to Paris along with a summer storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.76,0:23:19.26,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Gankutsuou,\NThe Count of Monte Cristo, act 3,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.16,0:23:20.17,count fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,350)}Act 3:\N5/22, Stormy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.26,0:23:21.49,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,..."5/22, Stormy".
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.63,0:23:23.66,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Bide your time,\nand hold out hope!
